snippet.title: Best VGM 2343 - I.Q. : Intelligent Qube - The 1st Tide
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 821 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nUiZp8hb42I

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
I.Q.: Intelligent Qube (1997)
The 1st Tide
Takayuki Hattori
